{"title":"Leecode_Q5：最长回文子串","uid":"db0f7d1c8657804301abbe296b7f8bdc","slug":"Leecode-Q5：最长回文子串","date":"2021-07-21T03:15:00.000Z","updated":"2021-07-21T03:50:45.423Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Leecode-Q5：最长回文子串.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"最长回文子串\"><a href=\"#最长回文子串\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"最长回文子串\"></a>最长回文子串</h1><p><b>题意描述：</b>给你一个字符串<code>s</code>，找到<code>s</code>中最长的回文子串</p>\n<p>这里官方给出的难度是中等，但对于我而言属于困难，为什么呢？困难的不是怎么解决问题，而是用一种高效的方式解决这个问题，首先最简单的方式就是暴力枚举，将所有的可能进行列举，假设一个左边界和一个右边界，最后还需要遍历判断字串，因此时间复杂度为<svg xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" width=\"6.76ex\" height=\"3.176ex\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.838ex;\" viewBox=\"0 -1006.6 2910.5 1367.4\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-labelledby=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">\n<title id=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">O(N^3)</title>\n<defs aria-hidden=\"true\">\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMATHI-4F\" d=\"M740 435Q740 320 676 213T511 42T304 -22Q207 -22 138 35T51 201Q50 209 50 244Q50 346 98 438T227 601Q351 704 476 704Q514 704 524 703Q621 689 680 617T740 435ZM637 476Q637 565 591 615T476 665Q396 665 322 605Q242 542 200 428T157 216Q157 126 200 73T314 19Q404 19 485 98T608 313Q637 408 637 476Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMAIN-28\" d=\"M94 250Q94 319 104 381T127 488T164 576T202 643T244 695T277 729T302 750H315H319Q333 750 333 741Q333 738 316 720T275 667T226 581T184 443T167 250T184 58T225 -81T274 -167T316 -220T333 -241Q333 -250 318 -250H315H302L274 -226Q180 -141 137 -14T94 250Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMATHI-4E\" d=\"M234 637Q231 637 226 637Q201 637 196 638T191 649Q191 676 202 682Q204 683 299 683Q376 683 387 683T401 677Q612 181 616 168L670 381Q723 592 723 606Q723 633 659 637Q635 637 635 648Q635 650 637 660Q641 676 643 679T653 683Q656 683 684 682T767 680Q817 680 843 681T873 682Q888 682 888 672Q888 650 880 642Q878 637 858 637Q787 633 769 597L620 7Q618 0 599 0Q585 0 582 2Q579 5 453 305L326 604L261 344Q196 88 196 79Q201 46 268 46H278Q284 41 284 38T282 19Q278 6 272 0H259Q228 2 151 2Q123 2 100 2T63 2T46 1Q31 1 31 10Q31 14 34 26T39 40Q41 46 62 46Q130 49 150 85Q154 91 221 362L289 634Q287 635 234 637Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMAIN-33\" d=\"M127 463Q100 463 85 480T69 524Q69 579 117 622T233 665Q268 665 277 664Q351 652 390 611T430 522Q430 470 396 421T302 350L299 348Q299 347 308 345T337 336T375 315Q457 262 457 175Q457 96 395 37T238 -22Q158 -22 100 21T42 130Q42 158 60 175T105 193Q133 193 151 175T169 130Q169 119 166 110T159 94T148 82T136 74T126 70T118 67L114 66Q165 21 238 21Q293 21 321 74Q338 107 338 175V195Q338 290 274 322Q259 328 213 329L171 330L168 332Q166 335 166 348Q166 366 174 366Q202 366 232 371Q266 376 294 413T322 525V533Q322 590 287 612Q265 626 240 626Q208 626 181 615T143 592T132 580H135Q138 579 143 578T153 573T165 566T175 555T183 540T186 520Q186 498 172 481T127 463Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMAIN-29\" d=\"M60 749L64 750Q69 750 74 750H86L114 726Q208 641 251 514T294 250Q294 182 284 119T261 12T224 -76T186 -143T145 -194T113 -227T90 -246Q87 -249 86 -250H74Q66 -250 63 -250T58 -247T55 -238Q56 -237 66 -225Q221 -64 221 250T66 725Q56 737 55 738Q55 746 60 749Z\"></path>\n</defs>\n<g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"matrix(1 0 0 -1 0 0)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <use xlink:href=\"#E1-MJMATHI-4F\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\"></use>\n <use xlink:href=\"#E1-MJMAIN-28\" x=\"763\" y=\"0\"></use>\n<g transform=\"translate(1153,0)\">\n <use xlink:href=\"#E1-MJMATHI-4E\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\"></use>\n <use transform=\"scale(0.707)\" xlink:href=\"#E1-MJMAIN-33\" x=\"1292\" y=\"583\"></use>\n</g>\n <use xlink:href=\"#E1-MJMAIN-29\" x=\"2520\" y=\"0\"></use>\n</g>\n</svg>，具体代码如下：</p>\n<p><b>暴力枚举法</b></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">def longestPalindrome(self, s: str) -&gt; str:\n    if len(s) &#x3D;&#x3D; 1:\n        return s\n    n &#x3D; len(s)\n    result &#x3D; s[0]\n    maxlen &#x3D; 0\n    for i in range(n - 1):\n        for j in range(i+1, n):\n            left &#x3D; i\n            right &#x3D; j\n            flag &#x3D; True\n            while left &lt; right:\n                if s[left] &#x3D;&#x3D; s[right]:\n                    left +&#x3D; 1\n                    right -&#x3D; 1\n                else:\n                    flag &#x3D; False\n                    break\n            if flag and j - i + 1 &gt; maxlen:\n                maxlen &#x3D; j - i + 1\n                result &#x3D; s[i:(j+1)]\n    return result</code></pre>\n\n<p><b>中心扩展法</b></p>\n<p><b>动态规划</b></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"最长回文子串题意描述：给你一个字符串s，找到s中最长的回文子串 这里官方给出的难度是中等，但对于我而言属于困难，为什么呢？困难的不是怎么解决问题，而是用一种高效的方式解决这个问题，首先最简单的方式就是暴力枚举，将所有的可能进行列举，假设一个左边界和一个右边界，最后还需要遍历判断字...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":892,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"刷题","slug":"刷题","count":5,"path":"api/categories/刷题.json"},{"name":"Leecode","slug":"刷题/Leecode","count":5,"path":"api/categories/刷题/Leecode.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Leecode","slug":"Leecode","count":5,"path":"api/tags/Leecode.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9C%80%E9%95%BF%E5%9B%9E%E6%96%87%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%B2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">最长回文子串</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Dominique Yiu","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/dominique-yiu/csdn/raw/master/theme/icon.png","link":"/","description":"There is only one heroism in the world, to see the world as it is and to love it. <br /> @ <b>realrealyiu@gmail.com</b>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Dominique-Yiu","twitter":"https://twitter.com/KingSwi39106371","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/whatever-36-86","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_49005782","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"Leecode：寻找两个正序数组的中位数","uid":"e28975790eb97ff1ceaf51d0